  [ Thomas Böhler ]
  * package: debian: strip headers package
  * package: debian: add missing Depends to linux-headers
  * package: debian: ignore package-has-long-file-name with lintian
  * package: debian: ignore lintian warning dbg-package-missing-depends

  [ Philipp Rosenberger ]
  * arm/dts/overlays: Add RevPi Connect 5 overlay stub
  * dts/connect5: Add gpio-line-names
  * dts/connect5: Add i2c1 configuration
  * dts/connect5: Add the io expander of the core board to i2c1
  * dts/connect5: Add the io expander of the power board to i2c1
  * dts/connect5: Add leds: PWR (red), A1..A5 (RGB)
  * dts/connect5: Add rtc (PCF2131) to i2c1
  * dts/connect5: Disable the rpi_rtc
  * dts/connect5: Add TPM (SLB 9670VQ2.0) to SPI1
  * dts/connect5: Add PiBridge uart (UART2) and sniff pins
  * dts/connect5: Add RS485 front interface at UART4
  * dts/connect5: Swap LED mode of SoC Ethernet
  * dts: Add Connect 5 with CAN controller (MCP251863)
  * dts: Add Connect 5 with 2xCAN controller (MCP251863)

  [ Lino Sanfilippo ]
